data.title: CONSTANCE Definition & Meaning
data.meta_description: Constance definition: a lake in W Europe, bounded by Germany, Austria, and Switzerland. 46 miles (74 km) long; 207 sq. mi. (536 sq. km).. See examples of CONSTANCE used in a sentence.
